Happy Monday! WOW. It’s been officially 12 years since I came to the States as an international student. I lived in Boston for about 6 months and I moved to LA. Life’s been a roller coaster ride since then! From getting scammed (while purchasing a car) to meeting my wife and having my own family, I’m grateful for all the experiences! I started MRVLSTYLE 7 years ago, and so grateful to be still doing what I’m really passionate about. I love creating content, and I’m always learning to be better. Thank you for following my journey and your continued support. 🙏🏻 
#internationalstudent #immigrantstories

I’m so excited to be partnering with my favorite custom dress shirt & clothing company @propercloth to share a special offer with you. (That can be found in the link in my bio!)
If you’ve been following me for a while, you know that almost all of my shirts are from them. Not only shirts, Proper Cloth is a pioneer and leader in quality custom-fit, made-to-order shirts, pants, jackets, and suits. So let’s talk about this specific shirt I custom made from them recently. Every season they develop a curated selection of fabrics from the world’s finest mills, pairing them with elegant design details that rival even the most prestigious luxury brands.

My exact customization for Duca Visconti Grey Supima Stretch Corduroy was, Soft Semi Spread Collar, Soft Long One Button Cuff, Rounded Pocket, Smoke Mother of Pearl Buttons, No Placket Front Placket, Split Yoke, Rounded Hem, with my VL monogram in navy. 

As you can see, each shirt is made-to-order to one’s precise specifications from the comfort of your home, quickly delivered to you! 
❗️Go to the link in my bio to check out my Custom Proper Cloth Closet. #ProperCloth

The pants, and coat are also from @propercloth 
.
.
.
#customshirts #custommade #customclothing #madetoorder #menswear #menstyle #mensstyle #mensfashion
